What do we mean that &ldquo;fire is hot?&rdquo;
Fire has a dividing or cutting power on our bodies. We all feel that fire is sharp. We may further consider:
 the fineness of the sides of fire the sharpness of the angles of fire the smallness of the particles of fire, and the swiftness of the motion of fire  All this makes the action of fire violent and sharp, so that it cuts whatever it meets.
